OL,3,CKing starts Bermuda visit with boat
OL,4,Ctrip, dancing and slavery exhibit
OL,6,FThe King was welcomed to Bermuda with
OL,7,Fa boat trip, dancing and a slavery
OL,8,Fexhibition, in his first trip to a
OL,9,FBritish overseas territory as monarch.
OL,11,FCharles kicked off his official visit
OL,12,Fon Friday with a ceremony at the
OL,13,Fterritory's former capital St
OL,14,FGeorge's, where a 21-gun salute
OL,15,Fheralded his arrival at the aptly
OL,16,Fnamed King's Square.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
