OL,3,CKing starts Bermuda visit with boat
OL,4,Ctrip, dancing and slavery exhibit
OL,6,FCharles then went to meet the crowds,
OL,7,Fshaking hands with well-wishers as the
OL,8,Fmilitary band played Bob Marley and
OL,9,Fthe Wailers song Jamming.
OL,11,FLater, he watched the release of an
OL,12,FAtlantic seabird after being ringed
OL,13,Fand joked, "it's bound to land on my
OL,14,Fhead".
OL,26,@uD@LOUvD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
