PN,31710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777914346
OL,3,CKing starts Bermuda visit with boat
OL,4,Ctrip, dancing and slavery exhibit
OL,6,FCharles later spoke during a reception
OL,7,Fin the garden of Government House in
OL,8,FHamilton, where he met Bermudian
OL,9,Ffootball player Clyde Best and
OL,10,Freceived a toast from Governor of
OL,11,FBermuda, Andrew Murdoch.
OL,13,FCharles's arrival in Bermuda on
OL,14,FThursday evening came after a four-day
OL,15,Fstate visit to America, where he
OL,16,Fhelped put the UK-US special
OL,17,Frelationship on a firmer footing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777914346
OL,3,CKing starts Bermuda visit with boat
OL,4,Ctrip, dancing and slavery exhibit
OL,6,FThe monarchy's soft power diplomacy is
OL,7,Fseen as its strongest weapon in
OL,8,Fsupport of the UK's overseas interests
OL,9,Fand it appears his host President
OL,10,FDonald Trump was won over.
OL,12,FA parting gift came from the US leader
OL,13,Fwho lifted tariffs on Scottish whisky
OL,14,Fafter an intervention by the Queen and
OL,15,FKing.
OL,17,FCharles is expected to end his visit
OL,18,Fto Bermuda by officially launching the
OL,19,FUK Space Agency's (UKSA) Project Nova
OL,20,Fto help track space debris.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
