FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1777914346
OL,3,CKing starts Bermuda visit with boat
OL,4,Ctrip, dancing and slavery exhibit
OL,6,FThe King will visit the site of a new
OL,7,FUKSA observatory on the island to hear
OL,8,Fabout the initiative to oversee the
OL,9,Finstallation of a global network of
OL,10,Ftelescopes, across five sites, to help
OL,11,Ftrack old satellites, rocket stages,
OL,12,Fand other objects.
OL,14,FThis is the Talking Royals - our
OL,15,Fweekly podcast about the Royal Family,
OL,16,Fwith ITV News Royal Editor Chris Ship
OL,17,Fand Producer Lizzie Robinson.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/12
